^ Karl G. Jansky, "Radio waves from outside the solar system", Nature, 132, p.66. 1933
^ http://www.nrao.edu/whatisra/hist_reber.shtml
^ J. S. Hey. The Radio Universe, 2nd Ed., Pergamon Press, Oxford-New York (1975),










